text.textblock: On February 10, 1993, the Department of Transportation's (DOT) Office of Commercial Space Transportation (OCST) conducted a public meeting for the purpose of gathering information relating to the low earth orbit (LEO) space market. Notice of the meeting was published in the

Written submissions provided to OCST at the meeting or in response to the Notice are available for public inspection under Docket No. 49416, in room 4107.
